OL,5,V5CZXGUESSER'S LOCKDOWN VENISON       Vj
OL,6,V5C                                   Vj
OL,7,V5CIngredients:GFrozen venison 2-yearsVj
OL,8,V5Gpast use-by date; 6 slightly manky Vj
OL,9,V5Gmushrooms; \ onion; 2 carrots;     Vj
OL,10,V5GButternut squash; 3 small tomatoes;Vj
OL,11,V5GAssorted potatoes; Olive oil;      Vj
OL,12,V5GMixed aromatic pepper.             Vj
OL,13,V5G                                   Vj
OL,14,V5CMethod:FCut potatoes into wedges   Vj
OL,15,V5Fand roast in oil. Dice carrots and Vj
OL,16,V5Fequal quantity of squash and sweat Vj
OL,17,V5Fin butter in a saucepan. Fry the   Vj
OL,18,V5Fvenison for 3 minutes and transfer Vj
OL,19,V5Fto warm plate to rest. Fry onion   Vj
OL,20,V5Fand mushrooms. Add veg, chopped    Vj
OL,21,V5Ftomato, crushed garlic, and pepper.Vj
OL,22,V5FServe with plenty of red wine.     Vj
